{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d3d08b0924","title":"关于发动反对中国法西斯主义的宣传运动给董必武的电报","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"5063511653","index":0,"year":1943,"month":8,"day":11,"articleId":"d3d08b0924"}],"tags":[{"id":"d5cbd05390","name":"通讯","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji3","name":"毛泽东文集第三卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji3.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji3":{"comments":[{"id":"e9a034220b","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据中央档案馆保存的抄件刊印。"},{"id":"52c83fc2b4","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":22,"text":"董必武，当时任中共中央南方局副书记兼宣传部部长、统战部部长。"},{"id":"814e5fd10b","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924","index":2,"part_index":3,"offset":74,"text":"蒋，指蒋介石。"},{"id":"401a32b4aa","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924","index":3,"part_index":4,"offset":101,"text":"指《新华日报》和《群众》杂志。"}],"contents":[{"id":"90f6c5c2d2","type":"title","text":"关于发动反对中国法西斯主义的宣传运动给董必武的电报","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924"},{"id":"52c83fc2b4","type":"appellation","text":"董：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924"},{"id":"814e5fd10b","type":"paragraph","text":"甲、边区军事虽稍缓和，但国民党的武装准备并未放松，其宣传斗争则更加紧，各地参议会，新闻、文化、妇女等团体请解散中共电，已有十多处，中央社更发反共社论、专电动员舆论。不知重庆月来舆论如何？望电告。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924"},{"id":"401a32b4aa","type":"paragraph","text":"乙、此间除继续广播评《中国之命运》各文外，拟于八、九两月发动反中国法西斯主义的运动，通电全国，主张取消各种特务组织，严禁传播法西斯主义思想，以揭穿蒋记国民党实质，并教育自己。不久将有通电、文章广播，请预为准备。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924"},{"id":"c9c616cb1f","type":"paragraph","text":"丙、渝、桂文化界反压迫抗议事可行，惟望注意：一、除少数知名之士外，不要暴露隐藏的文化人。二、发表的形式可采取多样的。三、尽量争取中间人，在中间刊物发表抗议。四、译成英文向美、英出版界揭露。五、新华、群众多登反法西斯主义文章，以开展思想斗争。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924"},{"id":"33366f581e","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东周恩来","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924"},{"id":"4d39549969","type":"paragraph","text":"真延","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924"}],"page":{"id":"a4e04658aa","publicationId":"wenji3","articleId":"d3d08b0924","start":75,"end":76}}}},"__N_SSG":true}